# PHASE 2 — Configure Supabase Side

## Step 6: Update Supabase Helm Values

```bash
# First get current Supabase values
helm get values supabase -n moizaleem21-dev > /tmp/current-supabase-values.yaml
cat /tmp/current-supabase-values.yaml
```

Create updated values file:

```bash
cat > environments/dev/supabase-keycloak-values.yaml << 'EOF'
# ============================================================
# Supabase Values — Keycloak Integration
# ============================================================

auth:
  # ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  # │  KEYCLOAK AS EXTERNAL JWT PROVIDER                  │
  # │  Supabase will trust tokens issued by Keycloak      │
  # └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

  # Disable Supabase built-in auth (we use Keycloak)
  enabled: true

  environment:
    # JWT Secret — must match what Keycloak uses
    # Generate: openssl rand -base64 32
    GOTRUE_JWT_SECRET: "your-jwt-secret-here"
    GOTRUE_JWT_EXP: 3600
    GOTRUE_JWT_DEFAULT_GROUP_NAME: "authenticated"

    # Keycloak as OIDC provider
    GOTRUE_EXTERNAL_KEYCLOAK_ENABLED: "true"
    GOTRUE_EXTERNAL_KEYCLOAK_CLIENT_ID: "supabase"
    GOTRUE_EXTERNAL_KEYCLOAK_SECRET: "your-client-secret-from-keycloak"
    GOTRUE_EXTERNAL_KEYCLOAK_REDIRECT_URI: "https://<supabase-route>/auth/v1/callback"

    # Keycloak URLs (replace with your actual route)
    GOTRUE_EXTERNAL_KEYCLOAK_URL: "https://<keycloak-route>/realms/aiops-dev"

    # Site URL (Supabase Studio URL)
    API_EXTERNAL_URL: "https://<supabase-route>"
    GOTRUE_SITE_URL: "https://<supabase-studio-route>"

    # Additional redirect URLs allowed
    GOTRUE_URI_ALLOW_LIST: "https://<supabase-studio-route>/*"

# ─── PostgREST — Row Level Security via JWT ───────────────
rest:
  environment:
    # This tells PostgREST to verify JWT tokens from Keycloak
    PGRST_JWT_SECRET: "your-jwt-secret-here"
    # Keycloak issuer URL
    PGRST_JWT_AUD: "supabase"

# ─── Kong API Gateway ─────────────────────────────────────
kong:
  environment:
    SUPABASE_ANON_KEY: "your-anon-key"
    SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY: "your-service-key"
EOF
```

